              <strong><a href="http://www.homei123.com" rel="external nofollow" class="url">快乐家园</a> <img src="http://www.arefly.com/wp-content/plugins/show-useragent/flags/cn.png" title="China" alt="China" class="country-flag" /> <img src="http://www.arefly.com/wp-content/plugins/show-useragent/browsers/safari.png" title="Safari 9537.53" alt="Safari" width="12" height="12" class="browser-icon" /> <img src="http://www.arefly.com/wp-content/plugins/show-useragent/browsers/ipad.png" title="iPad  OS 7_0_4 like Mac OS X" alt="iPad" width="12" height="12" class="os-icon" /> <a class="vip3" title="_人 LV.3"></a></strong>： 
             </div> 
             <p>等于1不太对。。用<code>if (isset($_POST['isajaxtype']) &amp;&amp; $_POST['isajaxtype'] &gt; -1) {</code><br /> 可以。另外有些ajax评论是没有err函数的，我的博客的评论打勾用我的这段代码正常</p> 
             <div class="clear"></div> 
             <span class="datetime"><time datetime="2014-01-18 15:11:33">2014-01-18 下午3:11</time> </span> 
